{"tid":117194,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"[突發] 清水富美加疑閃電引退","createTime":"2017-02-12T04:23:42.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-12T15:55:55.000Z","uid":1790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"c77962dbba134f630f79d1dcad09b55c000f1d00","tid":117194,"uid":1790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-12T04:23:42.000Z","msg":"轉自facebook<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1N56R7e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1N56R7e.jpg&h=07e319fb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n女星・清水富美加（２２）驚傳閃電引退！<br />\n　<br />\n<a href=\"http://headlines.yahoo.co.jp/hl?a=20170212-00000503-sanspo-ent\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fheadlines.yahoo.co.jp%2Fhl%3Fa%3D20170212-00000503-sanspo-ent&d=mZhSvp2BRS%2BtHw05K%2FyMFMn%2FdpYTMnF8ODxps2tmzCA%3D&h=3b13a400\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://headlines.yahoo.co.jp/hl?a=20170212-00000503-sanspo-ent</a><br />\n　<br />\n清水富美加（２２）昨天缺席了他固定演出的綜藝節目「にじいろ－」<br />\n當時電視畫面上只打出因清水因身體狀況不佳而缺席錄影<br />\n但是在今天有驚人的展開<br />\n據報導，清水已向所屬事務所表達今後將專心擔任他全家都信仰的宗教團體「幸福の科学」的職務，因此即日起將自藝能界引退<br />\n事務所雖然希望清水至少走完目前的合約後再離開，但是「幸福の科学」還是堅持清水要立刻退社，雙方會談沒有交集...<br />\n各大媒體目前都無法連絡上清水本人<br />\n　"},{"pid":"848fdf70287d944f5cbac8756b366daec9a5f6f0","tid":117194,"uid":1790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-12T04:24:32.000Z","msg":"好sad<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"52cba7c696bde7dc5f20fefeb7a0a899f5ed1088","tid":117194,"uid":20943,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-12T04:25:03.000Z","msg":"幸福科學教<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/31.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7e12f7ea197e2422ca390acf79f72819eb210546","tid":117194,"uid":60831,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-12T04:28:14.000Z","msg":"係咪即係入咗邪教呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/31.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"243b3592cbe18f0f93a4528c7c7eda1b5dcfe2ad","tid":117194,"uid":60170,"like":0,"dislike"